sentences: Yuvir Pillay (born 15 July 1989), better known by his stage name Sketchy Bongo, is a South African record producer, DJ and songwriter from Durban.
Yuvir Pillay grew up in KwaZulu-Natal, South Africa.
"All About It" (2016) - Sketchy Bongo and Jimmy Nevis
"Inside My Head" (2016) - Sketchy Bongo & Danny K
"Just Hang On" (2019) - Sketchy Bongo and Shenfm
